until his resistance to damage wore thin. The first blast penetrated his
left arm, then one shot through the shoulder with the blade ripping his arm
off. &quot;AAAAAAHHHHHHHHHHH&quot; Bounty yelled until a blast severed his neck
causing his head to fall to the ground. Eventually the attackers stopped
firing and the hole filled body fell to the ground nonfunctional. His spark
hovered out of his body and fell to the ground extinguishing itself. A last
flinch of neural discharge caused the body to jump one last time before
laying still forever.


